-- Transnet Freight Rail Says It Cut Amount of Cable Stolen Each Month by 52%
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-09-21T11:06:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/transnet-freight-rail-says-it-cut-amount-of-cable-stolen-each-month-by-52-.html
Transnet Ltd. said its freight rail
operations have reduced the amount of cable stolen each month by
52 percent compared with last year’s monthly averages.  Transnet, South Africa’s state-owned ports and freight rail
operator, commented in an e-mailed statement today. 